Find cheap flights, hotels & cars on BudgetAir.com

   Whether you're looking for a Cheap Flight, or a complete holiday
   package including Hotel and Car Rental, then look no further than
   BudgetAir. We are Travel specialists, and have the best deals around to
   make your travel easy and at the best price.

   Booking with BudgetAir is simple and fast. We compare all available
   options to give you the most convenient flights, hotels and cars at the
   best price. Just choose where you want to go. We do the searching for
   you, so you have more time to plan the rest of your trip.

   When you select your destination and travel dates, you will be shown
   all available options for your trip. You can refine your search by
   choosing specific airlines, or only non-stop flights. Once you have
   made your choice, you will be guided through a simple checkout process
   to pay for your trip. With BudgetAir, travel is made easy.

